<section class="Sh">
<h1 class="Sh" id="HISTORY"><a class="permalink" href="#HISTORY">HISTORY</a></h1>
The <code class="Nm">paxctl</code> utility first appeared in
  <span class="Ux">NetBSD 4.0</span>.
<p class="Pp">The <code class="Nm">paxctl</code> utility is modeled after a tool
    of the same name available for Linux from the PaX project.</p>
</section>
